GeneralText: 1. Number of Deaths, Years of Life Lost, Percent Increase, and Disparity Ratio: Fusion Center analysis prepared using CDPH Vital Statistics Death Data Files; 2007-2017.
2. Years Lived with Disability: Institute for Health metrics and Evaluation (IHME).  GBD Compare. Seattle, WA: IHME, University of Washington, 2015.
3. Infectious Disease: Center for Infectious Diseases, California Department of Public Health.
